like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T05:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64703f5f296a3f8c16f5fddad405bf8cbac957e5","tid":1866822,"uid":178746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"發現條友唔係屋企係咪可以做9佢先<br />\n係既就條條友都report 佢無自我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申收到email"},{"pid":"9e57e8c56ed986203aacc52785e324981f405881","tid":1866822,"uid":100871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"食衞局稱強制檢疫措施靠市民自律 入境後可自行回家<br />\n<br />\n所有由內地入境香港的人士被強制檢疫14天的措施，午夜起實施。食物及衞生局局長陳肇始說，<strong>近日確診個案反映家庭傳播風險高</strong>，<span style=\"color: red;\">不過她說，被強制檢疫人士的家人，不需要接受強制檢疫。</span><br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局副秘書長鄭鍾偉說，強制檢疫措施依靠市民<strong>自律很重要</strong>，有關人士入境本港後<strong>可以自行回家</strong>，衞生署員人和警方會抽查有關人士是否按規定接受檢疫，其家人則不受強制檢疫限制。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507301-20200207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507301-20200207.htm&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=ec81192d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507301-20200207.htm&h=d74994ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507301-20200207.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fb43c9f49b3c47d81c166bb65e8f2bdee1b5b2cb","tid":1866822,"uid":100871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hGw1AzTGCGFgMODACSWhnDzZuGzc_VAtbaA5JR1NWRmx1CgoLOV9RbSA5TjolDV8GZV5fPy86A2lyDlcJZAlR/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hGw1AzTGCGFgMODACSWhnDzZuGzc_VAtbaA5JR1NWRmx1CgoLOV9RbSA5TjolDV8GZV5fPy86A2lyDlcJZAlR%2Fw644&h=478314b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0abe4036a645cf3844d4afe547f5b32b1bea765","tid":1866822,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike"